## Including Plots

You can also embed plots, for example:

```{r, echo=FALSE}
plot_ly(economics, x = ~date, color = I("blue")) %>%
  add_lines(y = ~uempmed) %>%
  add_lines(y = ~psavert, color = I("red"))

```
